    <description><![CDATA[
        <h1>Festival (v.1.0.0)</h1>
        <div style="clear: both;"></div>
        <p></p>
        <p>Created by <a href="https://www.vfxhost.gr" target="_blank">Kyriakos Liarakos</a><br /><small>Development started 28th August, 2023</small></p>
